# Hosting (Cloudflare Pages)

## When this applies

User mentions **hosting**, **deploy**, **import repo**, **Cloudflare Pages**, or **Vercel-style** frontend deploy.

## What to do

1. Read [`docs/plans/voltbase-hosting-pages.md`](docs/plans/voltbase-hosting-pages.md)
2. Code lives in `apps/api/src/hosting/` and `apps/web/src/features/hosting/`
3. Requires `CF_ACCOUNT_ID` + `CF_API_TOKEN`; GitHub OAuth for repo list
4. Free Pages soft-cap ~95 projects; Next SSR needs Workers/OpenNext (phase 2)

## Locked decisions

- Nest builds + Cloudflare Pages Direct Upload (multi-tenant on Free)
- Auto-inject Voltbase URL + anon key
- Vercel-style Import → Build theater → Ready UX
